ds/2014/09/P14110051.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6431 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110051-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110051" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6446 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115012-1024x682.jpg" alt="P14115012" width="1024" height="682" /></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110053.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6432 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110053-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110053" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110056.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6433 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110056-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110056" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110060.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6435 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110060-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110060" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110061.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6436 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110061-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110061" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110062-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6437 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110062-1-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110062 (1)" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110062.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6438 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110062-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110062" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110063.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6439 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110063-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110063" width="1024" height="678" /></a></p><p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6434 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14110059-1024x678.jpg" alt="P14110059" width="1024" height="678" /></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115011.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6445 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115011-1024x682.jpg" alt="P14115011" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115015.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6447 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115015-1024x682.jpg" alt="P14115015" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115016.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6448 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14115016-1024x682.jpg" alt="P14115016" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>Derechos de imágenes: Centro PSA Madrid.</p> ";}s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:52:"http://citronoticias.com/fabricacion-c4-cactus/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:1:"0";}s:7:"summary";s:177:"¿Te has preguntado cómo se fabrica el Citroën C4 Cactus en la planta de PSA Madrid? ¡Descúbrelo mediante las siguientes imágenes! Derechos de imágenes: Centro PSA Madrid.";s:12:"atom_content";s:7675:"<p>¿Te has preguntado cómo se fabrica el Citroën C4 Cactus en la planta de PSA Madrid? ¡Descúbrelo mediante las siguientes imágenes!</p><p><a href="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14116003.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-6449 size-large" src="http://citronoticias.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/P14116003-1024x682.jpg" alt="P14116003" width="1024" height="682" /></